# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BCD-MDI primary-core reaction smoke test
# Reaction: BCD-OH + O=C=N-MDI -> urethane
#
# Run from inside reaction_templates_primary_core/:
#   lmp -in in.primary_core
